@startuml
actor "Khách hàng" as User
participant "ProfileService" as Frontend
participant "UserController" as Controller
participant "UserServiceImpl" as Service
participant "IBookingRepository" as BookingRepo
participant "IPaymentRepository" as PaymentRepo

User -> Frontend: 1. Vào tab Lịch sử đặt phòng
Frontend -> Controller: 2. GET /api/users/me/bookings
Controller -> Service: 3. getMyBookingHistory(username)
Service -> BookingRepo: 4. findByCustomerUserIDOrderByBookingDateDesc(userId)
loop Mỗi booking
    Service -> Service: 5. syncExpiredBooking(booking)
end
Service -> Service: 6. map → List<BookingHistoryResponse> (toBookingHistory)
Service --> Controller: 7. List<BookingHistoryResponse>
Controller --> Frontend: 8. JSON
Frontend -> Frontend: 9. renderBookingHistory() → tạo article.booking-item
Frontend --> User: 10. Hiển thị đầy đủ lịch sử booking
@enduml